articles.title: U.S. Chamber of Commerce sues Trump administration over $100,000 H-1B visa fee - CNBC
articles.description: Trump recently imposed a $100,00 fee on temporary visas for highly skilled workers in a push to have American companies hire more domestic workers.
articles.content:
The U.S. Chamber of Commerce on Thursday filed a lawsuit over the Trump administration imposing a $100,000 fee to the H-1B worker visas.
